{"tid":1294863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民升級] 請提升你既技能","createTime":"2019-07-08T00:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T03:21:35.000Z","uid":40826,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64e13889f0de2c9ece76805ad7a25fd5dd28b531","tid":1294863,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"我發現好多手足打左幾場game仲係有技能不足既問題 所以寫左個list比大家參考下 觀迎補充<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">通用技能</span></span><br />\n1. 急救 (e.g. St. John first aid class)<br />\n2. 金/木工 (基本手動&amp;電動工具操作, 道具、裝備設計&amp;製作)<br />\n3. 手工藝 (道具、裝備設計&amp;製作)<br />\n4. 跑步 (要識點樣用氣先可以跑得耐 如果唔係好快冇氣)<br />\n5. 滅火、催淚彈<br />\n6. 英文 (被外國記者訪問既時候唔好連正常對答都做唔到)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">前線</span></span><br />\n1. 武器運用技巧 <br />\n2. 盾牌/防具運用技巧<br />\n3. 抗打擊能力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣/起底組</span></span><br />\n1. Photoshop/Illustrator (Poster, banner 等等設計)<br />\n2. Google (Google係你最好既朋友 但係好多人都用得唔好)<br />\n3. 「愛國愛黨」mode"},{"pid":"fae0713a0d64042f4f041a887da30fc348191395","tid":1294863,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:55:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ed7a6994402bbe7aa424ae030ac93051addf725","tid":1294863,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:57:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d28afd00b8e17274cdb1f8231d37bc10ed043ad","tid":1294863,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc0c0317c05393415f2b7c40d2082b3b7d14527","tid":1294863,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"c123b59da9b197af17ba63d9